metadata.name: PURPLE HAZE - ref 18GRJHS0001
metadata.description:
This NFT is tied to its physical counterpart, a portrait of Jimmy Hendrix named PURPLE HAZE ref 18GRJHS0001, 1mx81cm, mixed technique on canvas by the artist UNO8. 

The owner of this NFT owns the physical artwork and one can't be sold without the other. 

Shipping fees are not included in the price
